OL,3,CRunner pays tribute to partner who
OL,4,Cdied aged 35 with marathon for Marie
OL,5,CCurie
OL,7,FDarren Whitley ran the TCS London
OL,8,FMarathon with his partner four years
OL,9,Fago but, after her death at the age of
OL,10,F35, he will run this year while
OL,11,Ffundraising for the charity which
OL,12,Fsupported them in her final days.
OL,14,FA Marie Curie nurse cared for Jess
OL,15,FRoberts, who had been diagnosed with
OL,16,Fterminal cancer, at their home
OL,17,Fovernight before her death later that
OL,18,Fafternoon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776477807
OL,3,CRunner pays tribute to partner who
OL,4,Cdied aged 35 with marathon for Marie
OL,5,CCurie
OL,7,FMr Whitley, 36, of Stourbridge, West
OL,8,FMidlands, said he took Ms Roberts home
OL,9,Ffrom Russells Hall Hospital, Dudley,
OL,10,Fwhen there was a steep decline in her
OL,11,Fcondition after the cancer spread to
OL,12,Fher brain.
OL,14,FHe wanted her to spend her final hours
OL,15,Fat home and with their beloved dog
OL,16,FCalvin.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776477807
OL,3,CRunner pays tribute to partner who
OL,4,Cdied aged 35 with marathon for Marie
OL,5,CCurie
OL,7,FFamily and friends visited to say a
OL,8,Ffinal goodbye and Marie Curie nurse
OL,9,FMichelle stayed by Ms Roberts' bed,
OL,10,Fcaring for her, talking to her and
OL,11,Fbeing an "incredibly calming
OL,12,Finfluence", Mr Whitley told the Press
OL,13,FAssociation.
OL,15,FHe said he knew they were "in good
OL,16,Fhands", adding: "It was like, for that
OL,17,Fperiod of time, like having an
OL,18,Fincredibly good friend there, a
OL,19,Fselfless friend as well."
OL,26,@sD@JOUtD@JO]wD@[OUxD@FO]xD@QOU{D@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
