OL,3,CRunner pays tribute to partner who
OL,4,Cdied aged 35 with marathon for Marie
OL,5,CCurie
OL,7,FHe said Ms Roberts, who died on April
OL,8,F13 2024, was "the most incredible
OL,9,Fperson I've ever met".
OL,11,FThey had mutual friends and chatted on
OL,12,FFacebook before meeting in person in
OL,13,F2017 and starting a relationship,
OL,14,Fmoving in together after about six
OL,15,Fmonths.
OL,26,@pD@NOUqD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776477807
OL,3,CRunner pays tribute to partner who
OL,4,Cdied aged 35 with marathon for Marie
OL,5,CCurie
OL,7,FMs Roberts, from Dudley, was an
OL,8,Foptical assistant with Vision Express
OL,9,Fand he said: "She was incredibly hard-
OL,10,Fworking but, when it came to life, she
OL,11,Futilised that to the full, whether it
OL,12,Fwas a weekend she had off, the
OL,13,Fholidays we went on."
OL,15,FLess than a year after they got
OL,16,Ftogether, 29-year-old Ms Roberts found
OL,17,Fa lump in her breast, went for a
OL,18,Fmammogram and was diagnosed with stage
OL,19,Fthree breast cancer.
OL,26,@qD@NOUuD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776477807
OL,3,CRunner pays tribute to partner who
OL,4,Cdied aged 35 with marathon for Marie
OL,5,CCurie
OL,7,FShe had about five months of
OL,8,Fchemotherapy, a mastectomy,
OL,9,Freconstruction and a course of
OL,10,Fradiotherapy.
OL,12,FThey had to cancel a birthday trip to
OL,13,FRome so instead got Calvin, a cavapoo.
OL,15,F"He's been there through all of it.
OL,16,FWhen I had to go to work, he could
OL,17,Fstay at home with Jess," Mr Whitley
OL,18,Fsaid.
OL,26,@wD@AOUyD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
