OL,3,CRunner pays tribute to partner who
OL,4,Cdied aged 35 with marathon for Marie
OL,5,CCurie
OL,7,FMs Roberts used the experience "to
OL,8,Freshape herself, throw herself into
OL,9,Flife", Mr Whitley said and in December
OL,10,F2018, she was given the all-clear.
OL,12,FThe couple celebrated with a holiday
OL,13,Fto Thailand and, in 2019, Mr Whitley
OL,14,Fran the London Marathon for the
OL,15,FInstitute of Cancer Research.
OL,17,FHolidays to the US, Paris and Mexico
OL,18,Ffollowed and, in 2022, Ms Roberts ran
OL,19,Fthe London Marathon for the charity
OL,20,FBreast Cancer Care.
OL,26,@oD@`OUqD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776477807
OL,3,CRunner pays tribute to partner who
OL,4,Cdied aged 35 with marathon for Marie
OL,5,CCurie
OL,7,FMr Whitley caught up with her after
OL,8,Fseven miles so they could run the
OL,9,Fremainder of the 26.2 mile course
OL,10,Ftogether.
OL,12,F"Because she'd seen me do it, she
OL,13,Fwanted to do it to tick it off, a bit
OL,14,Fof a bucket list to say 'look I've
OL,15,Fdone this' and almost as a bit of an
OL,16,Finspiration to others," he said.
OL,18,FHe added: "At that point she had made
OL,19,Fa recovery, everything was behind her.
OL,26,@tD@AOUxD@WO]zD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776477807
OL,3,CRunner pays tribute to partner who
OL,4,Cdied aged 35 with marathon for Marie
OL,5,CCurie
OL,7,F"Confirmation that you've run a
OL,8,Fmarathon was almost closure on that
OL,9,Fprevious journey."
OL,11,FBut devastating news faced them in
OL,12,FSeptember the following year when,
OL,13,Fduring a trip to Dublin, Ms Roberts
OL,14,Fhad a bad cough which would not go
OL,15,Faway.
OL,17,FShe was treated for fluid on the lungs
OL,18,Fbefore tests showed it was secondary
OL,19,Fbreast cancer and had spread to her
OL,20,Flungs and liver.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776477807
OL,3,CRunner pays tribute to partner who
OL,4,Cdied aged 35 with marathon for Marie
OL,5,CCurie
OL,7,FMr Whitley said it felt as though they
OL,8,Fwere "back to day one", just when they
OL,9,Fhad believed that chapter of their
OL,10,Flives was over.
OL,12,FMs Roberts was told she was stage four
OL,13,Fand the cancer was terminal although
OL,14,Fshe could potentially have years left
OL,15,Fto live.
OL,17,FBut after several more rounds of
OL,18,Fchemotherapy, doctors said there was
OL,19,Fnothing more they could do.
OL,26,@pD@FOUpD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776477807
OL,3,CRunner pays tribute to partner who
OL,4,Cdied aged 35 with marathon for Marie
OL,5,CCurie
OL,7,FThey spent Christmas together and went
OL,8,Fto Disneyland Paris in early 2024
OL,9,Fwhere Mr Whitley said she managed
OL,10,Fthree full days on her feet.
OL,12,F"She's always been the biggest kid at
OL,13,Fheart," he said. "Up until the end, it
OL,14,Fwas all about living her life."
OL,16,FSoon afterwards, Ms Roberts' health
OL,17,Fwent downhill. She became confused and
OL,18,Fwas no longer independent. Doctors
OL,19,Ftold them the cancer had spread to her
OL,20,Fbrain.
OL,26,@tD@AOUuD@GO]uD@ROUvD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776477807
OL,3,CRunner pays tribute to partner who
OL,4,Cdied aged 35 with marathon for Marie
OL,5,CCurie
OL,7,FMr Whitley took her home on Thursday
OL,8,FApril 11 and the next day he called
OL,9,FMarie Curie who sent nurse Michelle to
OL,10,Fcare for Ms Roberts for 12 hours
OL,11,Fthrough the night so Mr Whitley and Ms
OL,12,FRoberts' mother Joanna could get some
OL,13,Frest.
OL,15,F"I cannot speak highly enough of Marie
OL,16,FCurie," he said. "It's incredible what
OL,17,Fthey do.
OL,19,F"You've got that incredibly calming
OL,20,Finfluence as well.
OL,26,@wD@AOUxD@GO]xD@ROU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776477807
OL,3,CRunner pays tribute to partner who
OL,4,Cdied aged 35 with marathon for Marie
OL,5,CCurie
OL,7,F"A Marie Curie nurse has got the
OL,8,Fknowledge and the bedside manner as
OL,9,Fwell.
OL,11,F"They were able to know what to check
OL,12,Fwhen, know where things were, know if
OL,13,Fshe was OK or not, talk to her.
OL,15,F"It gave us a couple of hours sleep,
OL,16,Fknowing she was in good hands."
OL,18,FHe slept on the sofa while Michelle
OL,19,Fwas at Ms Roberts' bedside and he
OL,20,Fsaid: "She never moved from there. Her
OL,21,Fsole priority was Jess."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUwD@AOUxD@_O]|D@GOU}D@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30414
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776477807
OL,3,CRunner pays tribute to partner who
OL,4,Cdied aged 35 with marathon for Marie
OL,5,CCurie
OL,7,FThe next day Ms Roberts was seen by
OL,8,Fcommunity nurses and she died at
OL,9,F4.10pm with Calvin next to her.
OL,11,FA photo of her will be on Darren's top
OL,12,Fwhen he runs the TCS London Marathon
OL,13,Fon Sunday April 26 while raising money
OL,14,Fto help Marie Curie support others
OL,15,Flike Ms Roberts and their families.
OL,17,FA donation of #23 can help to pay for
OL,18,Fan hour of vital nursing care for
OL,19,Fsomeone living with a terminal illness.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30415
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776477807
OL,3,CRunner pays tribute to partner who
OL,4,Cdied aged 35 with marathon for Marie
OL,5,CCurie
OL,7,FMr Whitley, who works in banking, also
OL,8,Fwants to encourage other people to
OL,9,Fapproach Marie Curie if they find
OL,10,Fthemselves in a similar situation.
OL,12,F"It's not an admittance that you can't
OL,13,Fdo it. It's purely there to help you
OL,14,Fand support you."
OL,16,FIt will be his sixth marathon and
OL,17,Ffourth time running London. He has
OL,18,Falso run marathons in Stratford and
OL,19,FBirmingham.
OL,26,@tD@AOUvD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30416
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776477807
OL,3,CRunner pays tribute to partner who
OL,4,Cdied aged 35 with marathon for Marie
OL,5,CCurie
OL,7,FHis first marathon since losing Ms
OL,8,FRoberts will be full of memories of
OL,9,Fwhen they ran together in 2022.
OL,11,F"This will actually be the first one
OL,12,Fthat she won't have been at. She's
OL,13,Fbeen at all of the London ones
OL,14,Fpreviously," he said.
OL,16,F"She always brought the best out of
OL,17,Fme."
OL,26,@sD@AOUvD@LO]xD@AOUyD@DO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/16
